          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1600444882394-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>medium egg noodles</strong> to a pot and cover with<strong> boiled water </strong>until fully submerged</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 5-6 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain and set aside</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
